{
  "text": "The maintenance of the subtropical jet in the presence of baroclinic eddies, however, is less clear. An analysis of the zonal momentum balance shows why this is not trivial. The zonal momentum budget in the upper troposphere is close to satisfying the following equation for the zonal mean momentum in steady state [CITATION_1] :",
